txt.en: You have encountered a warband of vicious crebain led by Gundul, a hardy half-orc of Isengard.
You have defeated Gundul along with his flock of crebain and brought a moment of peace to the struggling Free Peoples of Garsfeld.
You have discovered a warband of vicious crebain led by a hardy Half-orc of Isengard. Garsfeld cannot survive as long as he and his band stalk the field.
You have discovered a warband of vicious crebain led by a hardy Half-orc of Isengard.
Gundul and his crebain can be found roaming the fields and roads to the east of Garsfeld.
